{"tid":943448,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【雪廠街又贏】立法會宣誓DQ 同 英美做法相提並論？ 比卡超秒殺11哥","createTime":"2018-12-16T14:12:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-17T10:47:28.000Z","uid":138409,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"afe5855bb557c2c467bbe14d1882465481748318","tid":943448,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T14:12:13.000Z","msg":"屌你臨記都係演員<br />\n畀啲掙扎好無<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n次次都係咁 你唔悶我都悶啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbtw比卡超<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/EdInDisguise/posts/2005259846253956\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FEdInDisguise%2Fposts%2F2005259846253956&d=SVKyMDPYAi9ihM%2BgfZNzZdZqoKrPvqrE%2FsQ53lv%2BkYo%3D&h=9e7f1b68\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/EdInDisguise/posts/2005259846253956</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TXqOiYR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTXqOiYR.jpg&h=26cf18dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7Cv27Sa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7Cv27Sa.jpg&h=fd2235d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OoHEqDP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOoHEqDP.jpg&h=35b3c37c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KdjvxiO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKdjvxiO.jpg&h=a464f607&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">tldr版</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">英國做法：</span><br />\n在英聯邦以英女皇為元首的國家中，要成為公民雖然必須宣誓效忠英女皇及其子嗣，但該誓言並非實質上強迫公民認可王室對國家實施的主權，而<span style=\"color: red;\">只是一個象徵式的規定，其實質要求只可限於要求宣誓人不以暴力革命的手段推翻政府</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">美國做法：</span><br />\n效忠宣誓的規定<span style=\"color: red;\">並無施加任何具體的責任予宣誓者</span>，因為宣誓效忠的對象並非任何時候的當權者，而只是「憲政的運作」<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">無人有權測試一名合法當選的立法機關成員，是否真誠地向憲法效忠</span>，因此舉等同政見審查，違反言論自由，特別是考慮到立法機關成員身為民意代表，比一般公民更需享有討論各種不同及具爭議性的政見的自由。<br />\n甚至乎<span style=\"color: red;\">若有參選人只是從概念上支持甚或倡議以武力抵抗政權，並無違反效忠誓言在這方面的要求，當局無權禁止對民主制度無即時威脅的人行使憲法權利參與公職人員選舉</span>"},{"pid":"e82c2fd3f4b334ca1c8cff4e76ce58b92a97dd45","tid":943448,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T14:15:16.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02ef0ca31656e12bc1fc9f30806557fd1d48420f","tid":943448,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T14:17:51.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"0c7fa1f859ae82c788d8cf3805cdee907448ac7c","tid":943448,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T14:21:25.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"0423beba73f19c4853aa3df54fbd9c27325b0432","tid":943448,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T14:23:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f482afaf4132511ef70ecef31e54c7651000fdd5","tid":943448,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T14:29:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb1766bb4155b1dcf46a20ae89aa64b83aee810e","tid":943448,"uid":59283,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T14:31:21.000Z","msg":"tldr版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42f62e9ef6fc26918fc2b877414e95e250429a0d","tid":943448,"uid":125026,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T14:33:13.000Z","msg":"pikapika<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pi